+# Codex Writer Findings — PublicMenu Chain: publicmenu-260328-083047-385c
+
+## Findings
+1. [P1] Fix 1 — CartView still uses the old `Выдано` / `Заказано` split instead of `Сейчас` / `История` / `Новый заказ`. `todayMyOrders` is only partitioned into `servedOrders` and `activeOrders` at `CartView.jsx:351-374`, and the renderer still prints flat order lists with per-order badges under `Выдано` and `Заказано` at `CartView.jsx:456-529` and `CartView.jsx:772-845`. There is no urgency subgrouping (`Готов` -> `Готовится` -> `Принят`) or collapsed `История` summary row. FIX: replace the old served/active split with explicit `currentOrders` and `historyOrders` arrays based on the raw DB statuses from the task, group current orders by status priority, and render `История` as the collapsed summary block.
+2. [P1] Fix 2 — The visit total is still inside scrollable content, and the footer logic only handles the non-empty-cart submit state. `ИТОГО за визит` remains a normal card at `CartView.jsx:980-991`, while the sticky block at `CartView.jsx:1007-1041` appears only when `cart.length > 0` and never renders the required empty-cart or first-order variants (`ИТОГО`, `К отправке`, `Всего`, `Заказать ещё`). FIX: convert the drawer body to `flex flex-col h-full` with a scrollable content area and a persistent footer that switches copy/buttons by visit state, while keeping totals float-safe via `parseFloat(...toFixed(2))`.
+3. [P1] Fix 3 — Rating UI is still shown before delivery. Inside `renderOrderItems`, every item renders `<Rating>` whenever `reviewsEnabled` is true at `CartView.jsx:489-516`, regardless of `order.status`, and the only review CTA is the generic section button at `CartView.jsx:834-842` / `CartView.jsx:742-752` instead of a per-order `Оценить блюда` trigger for delivered orders. FIX: gate review UI by delivered statuses only, show a per-order `Оценить блюда` button for `Подано` / `Выдан гостю`, and expand the existing stars only after that CTA is tapped.
+4. [P1] Fix 4 — Orders in the active section are still fully expanded rows, not collapsed summaries. Each order renders its full item list immediately at `CartView.jsx:474-520`, with only time + badge in the header at `CartView.jsx:466-473`; there is no 2-item preview, `+N` remainder, per-order chevron, or collapsed/expanded state per active order. FIX: add per-order collapse state for `Сейчас`, render the summary row with the first two item names plus `+N` and the existing formatted total, then reveal the full item list on expand.
+5. [P2] Fix 5 — The old split toggle is still in place instead of the new guest selector. `splitSummary` still resolves to `На всех` / `Только я` at `CartView.jsx:450-452`, and the cart renders an inline `Для кого заказ` radio group at `CartView.jsx:904-970`, even when `canSplit` is false. There is no local sheet/popover picker and the selector is not hidden for single-guest tables. FIX: hide the control when `guestCount <= 1`, replace the inline radios with a local open/close guest picker, and surface the selected guest as `Кому заказ: ...`.
+6. [P2] Fix 6 — Guest-facing status copy is still the old set. `getSafeStatus` falls back to `Заказано` and `Готово` at `CartView.jsx:252-278`, and those labels are rendered directly in the badge at `CartView.jsx:470-472`. There is no display-layer mapping that turns `Заказано` / `Принято` into `Принят` or `Выдан гостю` into `Подано`. FIX: normalize display labels to `Принят`, `Готовится`, `Готов`, and `Подано` without changing the raw status values used for filtering.
+7. [P1] Fix 7 — The shift filter still uses midnight, not the 06:00 business-day cutoff. `todayMyOrders` compares `new Date(d).toDateString()` with today's date at `CartView.jsx:351-358`, so orders from the previous evening shift can still leak across midnight and early-morning orders can be misclassified. FIX: replace the date-only equality check with the rolling `today6am` cutoff described in the task, then run the existing newest-first sort on the filtered result.
+8. [P1] Fix 8 — The success screen total still passes the raw floating-point value to `formatPrice`. The confirmation footer renders `formatPrice(totalAmount)` at `x.jsx:726-731`, so totals like `31.00999999999998` can still appear. FIX: wrap the value with `parseFloat(totalAmount.toFixed(2))` before formatting.
+9. [P1] Fix 9 — Guest name persistence is global and never resets on table change. `guestNameInput` initializes from a single `menuapp_guest_name` key at `x.jsx:1358-1360`, writes back to the same key at `x.jsx:3161-3165`, and the current table identity is available as `currentTableId` at `x.jsx:1630-1634` but is never used to clear or scope the stored name. That leaves the stale-name regression in place for a new table/session. FIX: clear or namespace guest-name storage when `tableCodeParam` / `currentTableId` changes and fall back to `Гость` when no saved name exists.
+10. [P1] Fix 10 — The dedicated "all dishes delivered" state is missing. When only delivered orders remain, CartView still shows the regular collapsed `Выдано` section at `CartView.jsx:773-803`, the old `+ Добавить к заказу` button at `CartView.jsx:851-861`, and the generic visit-total / submit footer flow at `CartView.jsx:980-1041`. There is no `Все блюда поданы` banner, no `Дозаказать` primary CTA, and no `Попросить счёт` action/disabled fallback. FIX: add a D3 branch for `activeOrders.length === 0 && servedOrders.length > 0 && cart.length === 0`, render the special summary screen, and attach the sticky footer to the delivered-orders total.
